sentences.sentence: Deployments have grown longer and redeployments more frequent.
sentences.translation: 部署计划被延长，重新部署变得越来越频繁。

sentences.sentence: To most military analysts, these redeployments make a lot of sense.
sentences.translation: 在大多数军事分析家看来，这些重新部署十分在理。

sentences.sentence: Content and JAR file changes are not complete redeployments of the application.
sentences.translation: 内容和JAR文件的修改不足以完成应用程序的重新部署。
